{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T04:40:57.147Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the resources from Clawdbot/OpenClaw, AgentMail, and FAUN.dev, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Email-triggered agents (Clawdbot inbox clearing pattern)\""},{"type":"text","text":" is an "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"event-driven architecture where an AI agent automatically processes incoming emails, classifies them, drafts responses, and helps maintain a zero-inbox"},{"type":"text","text":"—turning email management into an automated workflow."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The pattern creates an "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"automated email triage and response system"},{"type":"text","text":" using OpenClaw (formerly Clawdbot) with Gmail Pub/Sub skills:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"New Email → Gmail Pub/Sub → Clawdbot Agent → Classify + Draft Response → Inbox Cleared"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Core Flow"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Email arrives in inbox\n   ↓\n2. Gmail Pub/Sub triggers webhook to Clawdbot\n   ↓\n3. Agent reads email (subject + body)\n   ↓\n4. Agent classifies category (urgent, action required, feedback, spam, etc.)\n   ↓\n5. Agent tags with label (Billing / Bug / Sales / Ops / etc.)\n   ↓\n6. Agent drafts response for human review\n   ↓\n7. Agent generates daily summary for managers\n   ↓\n8. Inbox stays organized until resolved"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Architecture Components"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Email Platform: AgentMail (Recommended)"}]},{"typ